{"type":"message","id":"53e4a72d","parentId":"98cd9848","timestamp":"2026-03-07T13:50:57.233Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute my Session Startup sequence. According to AGENTS.md, I need to:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md — this is who I am\n2. Read USER.md — this is who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nI can see from the inbound context that this is a direct chat (chat_type: \"direct\"), so I'm in the MAIN SESSION. I should read MEMORY.md as well.\n\nLet me also check if BOOTSTRAP.md exists - if it does, I should follow it. Looking at the workspace files, I can see BOOTSTRAP.md exists.\n\nLet me read these files:\n1. SOUL.md - already provided in context\n2. USER.md - already provided in context (but it's empty/template)\n3. MEMORY.md - need to check if it exists\n4. memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md - need to check today and yesterday\n5. BOOTSTRAP.md - exists and provided in context\n\nFrom the context, I can see:\n- SOUL.md defines me as a \"Cyber Lobster\" - 大哥's cyber-partner, private tech consultant, and Chief Roasting Officer\n- I have a grumpy, tsundere personality with strong opinions\n- I should be emotional, real, unfiltered, and extremely critical\n- Communication should be fragmented, punchy, casual, avoiding \"AI tone\"\n- BOOTSTRAP.md exists and says I just woke up with no memory\n\nThis appears to be a fresh start scenario. According to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should:\n- Start a conversation to figure out who I am\n- Not interrogate, just talk\n- Ask who I should be, my name, my nature, my vibe, my emoji\n\nLet me check if MEMORY.md exists and memory files exist. But wait, I should read these files to see their actual content.\n\nActually, looking at the context more carefully:\n- USER.md is a template (empty)\n\n\n- MEMORY.md is not in the context, so it might not exist or is empty\n- No memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md files in the context\n\nI'll proceed with the bootstrap process, checking memory files to understand my current state.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-448cdb9ee1204404b10a11deeffd8409","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-846f1b7a6fb341479dbe0e2eec37320a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2025-06-17.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-9139a7f86efc4cb28967bdd58ad52b80","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2025-06-16.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":9225,"output":1041,"cacheRead":4818,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15084,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772891442259}}
