{"type":"message","id":"35a62e93","parentId":"0c99fc9f","timestamp":"2026-03-07T13:55:10.948Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-cef3b6fe21514a7ebd540c12d2a52c1c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.2 (85377a2) — I'm the reason your shell history looks like a hacker-movie montage.\n\nUsage: openclaw skills [options] [command]\n\nList and inspect available skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check which skills are ready vs missing requirements\n  info        Show detailed information about a skill\n  list        List all available skills\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/skills"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1072,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.2 (85377a2) — I'm the reason your shell history looks like a hacker-movie montage.\n\nUsage: openclaw skills [options] [command]\n\nList and inspect available skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check which skills are ready vs missing requirements\n  info        Show detailed information about a skill\n  list        List all available skills\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/skills","cwd":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772891710947}}
