🌤️ weather       │ Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo.    │ openclaw-bundled   │\n│           │                  │ Use when: user asks about weather, temperature, or forecasts    │                    │\n│           │                  │ for any location. NOT for: historical weather data, severe      │                    │\n│           │                  │ weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API     │                    │\n│           │                  │ key needed.                                                     │                    │\n│ ✗ missing │ 𝕏 xurl           │ A CLI tool for making authenticated requests to the X           │ openclaw-bundled   │\n│           │                  │ (Twitter) API. Use this skill when you need to post tweets,     │                    │\n│           │                  │ reply, quote, search, read posts, manage followers, send DMs,   │                    │\n│           │                  │ upload media, or interact with any X API v2 endpoint.           │                    │\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 automation-    │ Design and implement automation workflows to save time and      │ openclaw-workspace │\n│           │ workflows        │ scale operations as a solopreneur. Use when identifying         │                    │\n│           │                  │ repetitive tasks to automate, building workflows across tools,  │                    │\n│           │                  │ setting up triggers and actions, or optimizing existing         │                    │\n│           │                  │ automations. Covers automation opportunity identification,      │                    │\n│           │                  │ workflow design, tool selection (Zapier, Make, n8n), testing,   │                    │\n│           │                  │ and maintenance. Trigger on \"automate\", \"automation\",           │                    │\n│           │                  │ \"workflow automation\", \"save time\", \"reduce manual work\",       │                    │\n│           │                  │ \"automate my business\", \"no-code automation\".                   │                    │\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 skill-vetter   │ Security-first skill vetting for AI agents. Use before          │ openclaw-workspace │\n│           │                  │ installing any skill from ClawdHub, GitHub, or other sources.   │                    │\n│           │                  │ Checks for red flags, permission scope, and suspicious          │                    │\n│           │                  │ patterns.                                                       │                    │\n│ ✗ missing │ 💎 obsidian-cli-  │ Official Obsidian CLI (v1.12+). Complete command-line           │ openclaw-workspace │\n│           │ official         │ interface for                                                   │                    │\n│           │                  │ Obsidian notes, tasks, search, tags, properties, links, and     │                    │\n│           │                  │ more.                                                           │                    │\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 proactive-     │ Transform AI agents from task-followers into proactive          │ openclaw-workspace │\n│           │ agent            │ partners that anticipate needs and continuously improve. Now    │                    │\n│           │                  │ with WAL Protocol, Working Buffer, Autonomous Crons, and        │                    │\n│           │                  │ battle-tested patterns. Part of the Hal Stack 🦞                 │                    │\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 qmd            │ Local search/indexing CLI (BM25 + vectors + rerank) with MCP    │ openclaw-workspace │\n│           │                  │ mode.                                                           │                    │\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 self-          │ Captures learnings, errors, and corrections to enable           │ openclaw-workspace │\n│      