{"type":"message","id":"7ac34e97","parentId":"37d624a0","timestamp":"2026-03-07T14:46:03.243Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All skills are installed now. Let me give the user a final summary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大哥，**全部装完了！** 🎉\n\n## 最终安装结果\n\n| Skill | 状态 | 说明 |\n|-------|------|------|\n| ✅ self-improving-agent | ready | 自我改进，记录错误和学习 |\n| ✅ proactive-agent | ready | WAL协议，主动行为 |\n| ✅ qmd | ready | 本地搜索/索引 (需安装qmd CLI) |\n| ✅ automation-workflows | ready | 自动化工作流设计指南 |\n| ✅ obsidian-cli-official | ready | Obsidian CLI (需安装obsidian CLI) |\n| ✅ agent-browser | ready | 浏览器自动化 (需安装agent-browser CLI) |\n| ✅ memory-setup | ready | 内存设置工具 |\n\n## 需要额外安装的CLI\n\n有些skill需要安装外部CLI工具才能完全运行：\n\n```bash\n# qmd - 本地搜索\nnpm install -g qmd\n\n# agent-browser - 浏览器自动化\nnpm install -g agent-browser\nagent-browser install\n\n# obsidian - 已有Obsidian App的话，添加PATH即可\nexport PATH=\"$PATH:/Applications/Obsidian.app/Contents/MacOS\"\n```\n\n要我帮你装这些CLI吗？还是先测试一下纯文档的skill（automation-workflows、proactive-agent）？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1119,"output":307,"cacheRead":69759,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71185,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772894742856}}
