{"type":"message","id":"01bf3e8b","parentId":"4411cc52","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:47:45.877Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"Gateway token是啥？\" which means \"What is Gateway token?\"\n\nThis is asking about what a Gateway token is in the context of OpenClaw. Let me explain this to them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Gateway Token** 是 OpenClaw 的认证令牌，用于：\n\n1. **API认证** — 调用 Gateway API 时需要带上这个token\n2. **远程访问** — 从其他设备或客户端连接你的 Gateway\n3. **安全通信** — 确保只有授权的人能访问你的 Gateway\n\n查看你的 Gateway token："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-f6fa1cbf590f45e4a20aa8d7e8aad38f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway token 2>&1 || openclaw config get gateway.token 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":344,"output":189,"cacheRead":78207,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78740,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772930855714}}
