{"type":"message","id":"9000e40a","parentId":"78f31572","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:49:08.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户需要 Gateway token 来配置 OpenClaw Browser Relay。让我查找一下这个 token 存储在哪里。\n\nGateway token 可能在以下几个地方：\n1. openclaw.json 配置文件\n2. paired.json 配对文件\n3. Gateway 启动时生成\n\n让我查看这些文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Gateway Token** 是 OpenClaw 的认证令牌，用于：\n\n1. **API认证** — 调用 Gateway API 时需要带上这个token\n2. **远程访问** — 从其他设备或客户端连接你的 Gateway\n3. **安全通信** — 确保只有授权的人能访问你的 Gateway\n\n查看你的 Gateway token："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-a0b68938f6c84f0c948af537a1884a1c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\ntry:\n    d = json.load(sys.stdin)\n    gw = d.get('gateway', {})\n    print('authToken:', gw.get('authToken', 'not found'))\n    print('token:', gw.get('token', 'not found'))\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('Error:', e)\n\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b28f7be447a142b8997dad3c79228093","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/paired.json 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\ntry:\n    d = json.load(sys.stdin)\n    for k, v in d.items():\n        if 'token' in str(k).lower() or 'token' in str(v).lower():\n            print(f'{k}: {v}')\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('Error:', e)\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":394,"output":387,"cacheRead":78655,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79436,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772945334155}}
