{"type":"message","id":"c9b8b711","parentId":"9aa1fd23","timestamp":"2026-03-08T05:11:30.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！让我给用户一个完整的总结。搞定！✅ **self-improving skill 已安装并跑通流程**\n\n## 安装完成\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| ✅ Skill 安装 | `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving/` |\n| ✅ 目录结构 | `~/self-improving/{projects,domains,archive}` |\n| ✅ 核心文件 | memory.md, corrections.md, index.md |\n| ✅ AGENTS.md 更新 | 添加了self-improving内存层级说明 |\n| ✅ SOUL.md 更新 | 添加了self-improving行为准则 |\n\n## 内存层级结构\n\n```\n~/self-improving/\n├── memory.md          # 🔥 HOT: ≤100行，总是加载\n├── corrections.md     # 最近50条修正记录\n├── index.md           # 主题索引\n├── projects/          # 项目特定学习\n├── domains/           # 领域特定（代码、写作、沟通）\n└── archive/           # ❄️ COLD: 归档模式\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n**检测到以下情况时自动记录：**\n- 用户纠正你 → 添加到 `corrections.md`\n- 明确的偏好信号 → 添加到 `memory.md`\n- 重复3次的模式 → 提升为规则\n\n**自我反思：**\n- 完成重要工作后，评估结果\n- 识别改进点\n- 记录为可复用的教训\n\n现在我已经可以：\n1. 从错误中学习\n2. 记录你的偏好\n3. 持续改进执行质量\n\n要测试一下吗？比如纠正我一个\"错误\"，看看我会不会记录？😄"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772946690240}}
