{"type":"message","id":"5c63e4c3","parentId":"22f36481","timestamp":"2026-03-08T06:22:56.261Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.exec:293","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"usage: cdp_publish.py [-h] [--host HOST] [--port PORT] [--headless]\n                      [--account ACCOUNT] [--timing-jitter TIMING_JITTER]\n                      [--reuse-existing-tab]\n                      {check-login,fill,publish,click-publish,search-feeds,search_feeds,get-feed-detail,get_feed_detail,post-comment-to-feed,post_comment_to_feed,get-notification-mentions,get_notification_mentions,content-data,content_data,login,re-login,switch-account,list-accounts,add-account,remove-account,set-default-account}\n                      ...\n\nXiaohongshu CDP Publisher\n\npositional arguments:\n  {check-login,fill,publish,click-publish,search-feeds,search_feeds,get-feed-detail,get_feed_detail,post-comment-to-feed,post_comment_to_feed,get-notification-mentions,get_notification_mentions,content-data,content_data,login,re-login,switch-account,list-accounts,add-account,remove-account,set-default-account}\n    check-login         Check login status (exit 0=logged in, 1=not)\n    fill                Fill title/content/images or video without publishing\n    publish             Fill form and click publish\n    click-publish       Click publish button on already-filled page\n    search-feeds (search_feeds)\n                        Search Xiaohongshu feeds by keyword\n    get-feed-detail (get_feed_detail)\n                        Get feed detail by feed id and xsec token\n    post-comment-to-feed (post_comment_to_feed)\n                        Post a top-level comment to feed detail\n    get-notification-mentions (get_notification_mentions)\n                        Capture notification mentions API payload from\n                        /notification page\n    content-data (content_data)\n                        Fetch creator content data table from statistics page\n    login               Open browser for QR code login (always headed mode)\n    re-login            Clear cookies and re-login same account (always\n                        headed)\n    switch-account      Clear cookies and open login page for new account\n                        (always headed)\n    list-accounts       List all configured accounts\n    add-account         Add a new account\n    remove-account      Remove an account\n    set-default-account\n                        Set the default account\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  --host HOST           CDP host (default: 127.0.0.1)\n  --port PORT           CDP remote debugging port (default: 9222)\n  --headless            Use headless Chrome (no GUI window)\n  --account ACCOUNT     Account name to use (default: default account)\n  --timing-jitter TIMING_JITTER\n                        Timing jitter ratio for operation delays (default:\n                        0.25). Set 0 to disable random jitter.\n  --reuse-existing-tab  Prefer reusing an existing tab before creating a new\n                        one. Useful in headed mode to reduce foreground focus\n                        switching."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":154,"aggregated":"usage: cdp_publish.py [-h] [--host HOST] [--port PORT] [--headless]\n                      [--account ACCOUNT] [--timing-jitter TIMING_JITTER]\n                      [--reuse-existing-tab]\n                      {check-login,fill,publish,click-publish,search-feeds,search_feeds,get-feed-detail,get_feed_detail,post-comment-to-feed,post_comment_to_feed,get-notification-mentions,get_notification_mentions,content-data,content_data,login,re-login,switch-account,list-accounts,add-account,remove-account,set-default-account}\n                      ...\n\nXiaohongshu CDP Publisher\n\npositional arguments:\n  {check-login,fill,publish,click-publish,search-feeds,search_feeds,get-feed-detail,get_feed_detail,post-comment-to-feed,post_comment_to_feed,get-notification-mentions,get_notification_mentions,content-data,content_data,login,re-login,switch-account,list-accounts,add-account,remove-account,set-default-account}\n    check-login         Check login status (exit 0=logged in, 1=not)\n    fill                Fill title/content/images or video without publishing\n    publish             Fill form and click publish\n    click-publish       Click publish button on already-filled page\n    search-feeds (search_feeds)\n                        Search Xiaohongshu feeds by keyword\n    get-feed-detail (get_feed_detail)\n                        Get feed detail by feed id and xsec token\n    post-comment-to-feed (post_comment_to_feed)\n                        Post a top-level comment to feed detail\n    get-notification-mentions (get_notification_mentions)\n                        Capture notification mentions API payload from\n                        /notification page\n    content-data (content_data)\n                        Fetch creator content data table from statistics page\n    login               Open browser for QR code login (always headed mode)\n    re-login            Clear cookies and re-login same account (always\n                        headed)\n    switch-account      Clear cookies and open login page for new account\n                        (always headed)\n    list-accounts       List all configured accounts\n    add-account         Add a new account\n    remove-account      Remove an account\n    set-default-account\n                        Set the default account\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  --host HOST           CDP host (default: 127.0.0.1)\n  --port PORT           CDP remote debugging port (default: 9222)\n  --headless            Use headless Chrome (no GUI window)\n  --account ACCOUNT     Account name to use (default: default account)\n  --timing-jitter TIMING_JITTER\n                        Timing jitter ratio for operation delays (default:\n                        0.25). Set 0 to disable random jitter.\n  --reuse-existing-tab  Prefer reusing an existing tab before creating a new\n                        one. Useful in headed mode to reduce foreground focus\n                        switching.","cwd":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772950976258}}
{"type":"message","id":"36b36744","parentId":"5c63e4c3","timestamp":"2026-03-08T06:23:11.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，所有脚本都可以正常运行了。让我给用户一个完整的总结。完美！✅ **xiaohongshuskills 安装完成并跑通流程**\n\n## 安装状态\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| ✅ Skill 文件 | `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/xiaohongshuskills/` |\n| ✅ Python 3.11 | `/opt/homebrew/bin/python3.11` |\n| ✅ 依赖包 | requests, websockets 已安装 |\n| ✅ Chrome启动器 | 可用 |\n| ✅ 发布脚本 | 可用 |\n\n## 核心功能\n\n**发布功能：**\n- 发布图文笔记\n- 发布视频笔记\n- 支持本地文件和URL\n\n**互动功能：**\n- 搜索笔记\n- 获取笔记详情\n- 发表评论\n- 查看通知和@\n\n**账号管理：**\n- 多账号切换\n- 扫码登录\n- Cookie管理\n\n## 快速测试\n\n```bash\n# 启动Chrome（有窗口模式）\n/opt/homebrew/bin/python3.11 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/xiaohongshuskills/scripts/chrome_launcher.py\n\n# 检查登录状态\n/opt/homebrew/bin/python3.11 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/xiaohongshuskills/scripts/cdp_publish.py check-login\n\n# 扫码登录\n/opt/homebrew/bin/python3.11 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/xiaohongshuskills/scripts/cdp_publish.py login\n```\n\n要我帮你登录测试一下，还是你自己来？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":13691,"output":329,"cacheRead":106624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120644,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772950976262}}
