{"type":"message","id":"c3797d6a","parentId":"4106ad1d","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:18:46.428Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.exec:299","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"npm warn exec The following package was not found and will be installed: skills@1.4.4\n\n[38;5;250m███████╗██╗  ██╗██╗██╗     ██╗     ███████╗[0m\n[38;5;248m██╔════╝██║ ██╔╝██║██║     ██║     ██╔════╝[0m\n[38;5;245m███████╗█████╔╝ ██║██║     ██║     ███████╗[0m\n[38;5;243m╚════██║██╔═██╗ ██║██║     ██║     ╚════██║[0m\n[38;5;240m███████║██║  ██╗██║███████╗███████╗███████║[0m\n[38;5;238m╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝╚══════╝╚══════╝╚══════╝[0m\n\n[38;5;102mInstall with[0m npx skills add <owner/repo@skill>\n\n[38;5;145msteipete/clawdis@weather[0m [36m877 installs[0m\n[38;5;102m└ https://skills.sh/steipete/clawdis/weather[0m\n\n[38;5;145mvikiboss/60s-skills@weather-query[0m [36m161 installs[0m\n[38;5;102m└ https://skills.sh/vikiboss/60s-skills/weather-query[0m\n\n[38;5;145mchandima/agent-skills@weather[0m [36m73 installs[0m\n[38;5;102m└ https://skills.sh/chandima/agent-skills/weather[0m"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5881,"aggregated":"npm warn exec The following package was not found and will be installed: skills@1.4.4\n\n[38;5;250m███████╗██╗  ██╗██╗██╗     ██╗     ███████╗[0m\n[38;5;248m██╔════╝██║ ██╔╝██║██║     ██║     ██╔════╝[0m\n[38;5;245m███████╗█████╔╝ ██║██║     ██║     ███████╗[0m\n[38;5;243m╚════██║██╔═██╗ ██║██║     ██║     ╚════██║[0m\n[38;5;240m███████║██║  ██╗██║███████╗███████╗███████║[0m\n[38;5;238m╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝╚══════╝╚══════╝╚══════╝[0m\n\n[38;5;102mInstall with[0m npx skills add <owner/repo@skill>\n\n[38;5;145msteipete/clawdis@weather[0m [36m877 installs[0m\n[38;5;102m└ https://skills.sh/steipete/clawdis/weather[0m\n\n[38;5;145mvikiboss/60s-skills@weather-query[0m [36m161 installs[0m\n[38;5;102m└ https://skills.sh/vikiboss/60s-skills/weather-query[0m\n\n[38;5;145mchandima/agent-skills@weather[0m [36m73 installs[0m\n