{"type":"message","id":"df55ffca","parentId":"c3797d6a","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:19:01.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，演示成功！现在让我给用户一个完整的总结。完美！✅ **find-skills 安装完成并跑通流程**\n\n## 安装状态\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| ✅ Skill 文件 | `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/find-skills/` |\n| ✅ Skills CLI | `npx skills` 可用 |\n\n## 核心功能\n\n**搜索 Skills：**\n```bash\nnpx skills find [关键词]\n```\n\n**安装 Skill：**\n```bash\nnpx skills add <owner/repo@skill> -g -y\n```\n\n**常用命令：**\n- `npx skills find react` — 搜索React相关\n- `npx skills find testing` — 搜索测试相关\n- `npx skills check` — 检查更新\n- `npx skills update` — 更新所有skills\n\n## 刚才演示\n\n搜索 \"weather\" 找到了3个相关skill：\n- steipete/clawdis@weather (877 installs)\n- vikiboss/60s-skills@weather-query (161 installs)\n- chandima/agent-skills@weather (73 installs)\n\n## 使用场景\n\n当你说：\n- \"怎么搞X\" → 我搜一下有没有skill\n- \"找个X的skill\" → 直接搜索安装\n- \"你能做X吗\" → 先搜skill，没有再直接做\n\n现在 **12个 skills** 全装好了！还要装别的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":13439,"output":309,"cacheRead":110464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124212,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772954326429}}
