{"type":"message","id":"c8a142cd","parentId":"113f4f20","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:43:01.672Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.exec:309","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\ntavily-search  Tavily Web Search\nSummary: AI-optimized web search via Tavily API. Returns concise, relevant results for AI agents.\nOwner: arun-8687\nCreated: 2026-01-11T07:02:00.544Z\nUpdated: 2026-03-02T16:57:47.584Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nTags: latest=1.0.0\nSelected: 1.0.0\nSelected At: 2026-01-11T07:02:00.544Z"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3757,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\ntavily-search  Tavily Web Search\nSummary: AI-optimized web search via Tavily API. Returns concise, relevant results for AI agents.\nOwner: arun-8687\nCreated: 2026-01-11T07:02:00.544Z\nUpdated: 2026-03-02T16:57:47.584Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nTags: latest=1.0.0\nSelected: 1.0.0\nSelected At: 2026-01-11T07:02:00.544Z","cwd":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772955781662}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac790171","parentId":"c8a142cd","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:43:58.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，Owner确实是arun-8687。现在让我读取SKILL.md并跑通流程。完美！Owner确实是 arun-8687。现在跑通流程："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"function.read:310","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace/skills/tavily-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":13270,"output":71,"cacheRead":112896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772955781672}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b4d0968","parentId":"ac790171","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:43:58.654Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.read:310","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: tavily\ndescription: AI-optimized web search via Tavily API. Returns concise, relevant results for AI agents.\nhomepage: https://tavily.com\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"🔍\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"node\"],\"env\":[\"TAVILY_API_KEY\"]},\"primaryEnv\":\"TAVILY_API_KEY\"}}\n---\n\n# Tavily Search\n\nAI-optimized web search using Tavily API. Designed for AI agents - returns clean, relevant content.\n\n## Search\n\n```bash\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\"\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" -n 10\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --deep\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --topic news\n```\n\n## Options\n\n- `-n <count>`: Number of results (default: 5, max: 20)\n- `--deep`: Use advanced search for deeper research (slower, more comprehensive)\n- `--topic <topic>`: Search topic - `general` (default) or `news`\n- `--days <n>`: For news topic, limit to last n days\n\n## Extract content from URL\n\n```bash\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/extract.mjs \"https://example.com/article\"\n```\n\nNotes:\n- Needs `TAVILY_API_KEY` from https://tavily.com\n- Tavily is optimized for AI - returns clean, relevant snippets\n- Use `--deep` for complex research questions\n- Use `--topic news` for current events\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772955838643}}
{"type":"message","id":"452bd07f","parentId":"9b4d0968","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:44:08.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，这个skill需要：\n1. Node.js（已安装）\n2. TAVILY_API_KEY（需要从tavily.com获取）\n\n让我检查一下scripts目录并测试。需要配置 API Key。让我检查脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"function.exec:311","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/tavily-search/scripts/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"function.read:312","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace/skills/tavily-search/scripts/search.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":13299,"output":109,"cacheRead":113280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126688,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772955838656}}
{"type":"message","id":"e362ff0f","parentId":"452bd07f","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:44:08.581Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.exec:311","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 16\ndrwx------  4 guruocen  staff   128 Mar  8 15:42 .\ndrwx------  6 guruocen  staff   192 Mar  8 15:42 ..\n-rw-------  1 guruocen  staff  1336 Mar  8 15:42 extract.mjs\n-rw-------  1 guruocen  staff  2299 Mar  8 15:42 search.mjs"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":24,"aggregated":"total 16\ndrwx------  4 guruocen  staff   128 Mar  8 15:42 .\ndrwx------  6 guruocen  staff   192 Mar  8 15:42 ..\n-rw-------  1 guruocen  staff  1336 Mar  8 15:42 extract.mjs\n-rw-------  1 guruocen  staff  2299 Mar  8 15:42 search.mjs","cwd":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772955848578}}
{"type":"message","id":"26e9e2f6","parentId":"e362ff0f","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:44:08.593Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.read:312","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n\nfunction usage() {\n  console.error(`Usage: search.mjs \"query\" [-n 5] [--deep] [--topic general|news] [--days 7]`);\n  process.exit(2);\n}\n\nconst args = process.argv.slice(2);\nif (args.length === 0 || args[0] === \"-h\" || args[0] === \"--help\") usage();\n\nconst query = args[0];\nlet n = 5;\nlet searchDepth = \"basic\";\nlet topic = \"general\";\nlet days = null;\n\nfor (let i = 1; i < args.length; i++) {\n  const a = args[i];\n  if (a === \"-n\") {\n    n = Number.parseInt(args[i + 1] ?? \"5\", 10);\n    i++;\n    continue;\n  }\n  if (a === \"--deep\") {\n    searchDepth = \"advanced\";\n    continue;\n  }\n  if (a === \"--topic\") {\n    topic = args[i + 1] ?? \"general\";\n    i++;\n    continue;\n  }\n  if (a === \"--days\") {\n    days = Number.parseInt(args[i + 1] ?? \"7\", 10);\n    i++;\n    continue;\n  }\n  console.error(`Unknown arg: ${a}`);\n  usage();\n}\n\nconst apiKey = (process.env.TAVILY_API_KEY ?? \"\").trim();\nif (!apiKey) {\n  console.error(\"Missing TAVILY_API_KEY\");\n  process.exit(1);\n}\n\nconst body = {\n  api_key: apiKey,\n  query: query,\n  search_depth: searchDepth,\n  topic: topic,\n  max_results: Math.max(1, Math.min(n, 20)),\n  include_answer: true,\n  include_raw_content: false,\n};\n\nif (topic === \"news\" && days) {\n  body.days = days;\n}\n\nconst resp = await fetch(\"https://api.tavily.com/search\", {\n  method: \"POST\",\n  headers: {\n    \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n  },\n  body: JSON.stringify(body),\n});\n\nif (!resp.ok) {\n  const text = await resp.text().catch(() => \"\");\n  throw new Error(`Tavily Search failed (${resp.status}): ${text}`);\n}\n\nconst data = await resp.json();\n\n// Print AI-generated answer if available\nif (data.answer) {\n  console.log(\"## Answer\\n\");\n  console.log(data.answer);\n  console.log(\"\\n---\\n\");\n}\n\n// Print results\nconst results = (data.results ?? []).slice(0, n);\nconsole.log(\"## Sources\\n\");\n\nfor (const r of results) {\n  const title = String(r?.title ?? \"\").trim();\n  const url = String(r?.url ?? \"\").trim();\n  const content = String(r?.content ?? \"\").trim();\n  const score = r?.score ? ` (relevance: ${(r.score * 100).toFixed(0)}%)` : \"\";\n  \n  if (!title || !url) continue;\n  console.log(`- **${title}**${score}`);\n  console.log(`  ${url}`);\n  if (content) {\n    console.log(`  ${content.slice(0, 300)}${content.length > 300 ? \"...\" : \"\"}`);\n  }\n  console.log();\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772955848584}}
