{"type":"message","id":"4ec0b4f0","parentId":"bff8c690","timestamp":"2026-03-08T11:40:02.285Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.exec:321","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\n#!/bin/bash\n# 小红书 MCP 环境检查脚本\n# 用法: bash ~/.openclaw/skills/xiaohongshu/check_env.sh\n\nMCP_URL=\"${XHS_MCP_URL:-http://localhost:18060/mcp}\"\nMCP_BIN=~/xiaohongshu-mcp/xiaohongshu-mcp-linux-amd64\n\necho \"=== 1. 检查 MCP 是否安装 ===\"\nif [ -x \"$MCP_BIN\" ]; then\n  echo \"✅ MCP 已安装\"\nelse\n  echo \"❌ MCP 未安装，请先执行安装流程\"\n  exit 1\nfi\n\necho \"=== 2. 检查 Xvfb 虚拟显示 ===\"\nif systemctl is-active --quiet xvfb 2>/dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ Xvfb 服务运行中 (systemd)\"\nelif pgrep -x Xvfb > /dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ Xvfb 运行中 (手动)\"\nelse\n  echo \"⚠️ Xvfb 未运行，尝试启动 systemd 服务...\"\n  systemctl start xvfb 2>/dev/null\n  sleep 1\n  if systemctl is-active --quiet xvfb 2>/dev/null; then\n    echo \"✅ Xvfb 服务已启动\"\n  else\n    echo \"⚠️ systemd 服务不存在，手动启动...\"\n    Xvfb :99 -screen 0 1920x1080x24 &\n    sleep 1\n    echo \"✅ Xvfb 已启动（非守护模式）\"\n  fi\nfi\n\necho \"=== 3. 检查 MCP 服务是否运行 ===\"\nif systemctl is-active --quiet xhs-mcp 2>/dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ MCP 服务运行中 (systemd 守护)\"\nelif pgrep -f xiaohongshu-mcp-linux > /dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ MCP 服务运行中 (手动)\"\nelse\n  echo \"⚠️ MCP 服务未运行，尝试启动 systemd 服务...\"\n  systemctl start xhs-mcp 2>/dev/null\n  sleep 2\n  if systemctl is-active --quiet xhs-mcp 2>/dev/null; then\n    echo \"✅ MCP 服务已启动 (systemd)\"\n  else\n    echo \"⚠️ systemd 服务不存在，手动启动...\"\n    cd ~/xiaohongshu-mcp && DISPLAY=:99 nohup ./xiaohongshu-mcp-linux-amd64 > mcp.log 2>&1 &\n    sleep 3"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4348,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\n#!/bin/bash\n# 小红书 MCP 环境检查脚本\n# 用法: bash ~/.openclaw/skills/xiaohongshu/check_env.sh\n\nMCP_URL=\"${XHS_MCP_URL:-http://localhost:18060/mcp}\"\nMCP_BIN=~/xiaohongshu-mcp/xiaohongshu-mcp-linux-amd64\n\necho \"=== 1. 检查 MCP 是否安装 ===\"\nif [ -x \"$MCP_BIN\" ]; then\n  echo \"✅ MCP 已安装\"\nelse\n  echo \"❌ MCP 未安装，请先执行安装流程\"\n  exit 1\nfi\n\necho \"=== 2. 检查 Xvfb 虚拟显示 ===\"\nif systemctl is-active --quiet xvfb 2>/dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ Xvfb 服务运行中 (systemd)\"\nelif pgrep -x Xvfb > /dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ Xvfb 运行中 (手动)\"\nelse\n  echo \"⚠️ Xvfb 未运行，尝试启动 systemd 服务...\"\n  systemctl start xvfb 2>/dev/null\n  sleep 1\n  if systemctl is-active --quiet xvfb 2>/dev/null; then\n    echo \"✅ Xvfb 服务已启动\"\n  else\n    echo \"⚠️ systemd 服务不存在，手动启动...\"\n    Xvfb :99 -screen 0 1920x1080x24 &\n    sleep 1\n    echo \"✅ Xvfb 已启动（非守护模式）\"\n  fi\nfi\n\necho \"=== 3. 检查 MCP 服务是否运行 ===\"\nif systemctl is-active --quiet xhs-mcp 2>/dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ MCP 服务运行中 (systemd 守护)\"\nelif pgrep -f xiaohongshu-mcp-linux > /dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ MCP 服务运行中 (手动)\"\nelse\n  echo \"⚠️ MCP 服务未运行，尝试启动 systemd 服务...\"\n  systemctl start xhs-mcp 2>/dev/null\n  sleep 2\n  if systemctl is-active --quiet xhs-mcp 2>/dev/null; then\n    echo \"✅ MCP 服务已启动 (systemd)\"\n  else\n    echo \"⚠️ systemd 服务不存在，手动启动...\"\n    cd ~/xiaohongshu-mcp && DISPLAY=:99 nohup ./xiaohongshu-mcp-linux-amd64 > mcp.log 2>&1 &\n    sleep 3","cwd":"/Users/guruocen/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772970002280}}
